#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Your rental duration was too short. Unfortunately, we do not process\n"
"                rentals that last less than %(duration)s %(unit)s.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                ໄລຍະເວລາການເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານສັ້ນເກີນໄປ. ຂໍອະໄພ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ສາມາດດຳເນີນການ\n"
"                ການເຊົ່າທີ່ມີໄລຍະເວລານ້ອຍກວ່າ %(duration)s %(unit)s.\n"
"            "

#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Your rental product had invalid date of pickup (%(start_date)s).\n"
"                Unfortunately, we do not process pickups on that weekday.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                ສິນຄ້າເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານມີວັນທີຮັບເຄື່ອງທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (%(start_date)s).\n"
"                ຂໍອະໄພ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ມີການບໍລິການຮັບເຄື່ອງໃນວັນດັ່ງກ່າວ.\n"
"            "

#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Your rental product had invalid date of return (%(end_date)s).\n"
"                Unfortunately, we do not process returns on that weekday.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                ສິນຄ້າເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານມີວັນທີສົ່ງຄືນທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (%(end_date)s).\n"
"                ຂໍອະໄພ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ມີການບໍລິການສົ່ງຄືນໃນວັນດັ່ງກ່າວ.\n"
"            "

#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Your rental product had invalid dates of pickup (%(start_date)s) and\n"
"                return (%(end_date)s). Unfortunately, we do not process pickups nor\n"
"                returns on those weekdays.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                ສິນຄ້າເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານມີວັນທີຮັບ (%(start_date)s) ແລະ ວັນທີສົ່ງຄືນ\n"
"                (%(end_date)s) ທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ຂໍອະໄພ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ມີການບໍລິການຮັບ ຫຼື\n"
"                ສົ່ງຄືນເຄື່ອງໃນວັນດັ່ງກ່າວ.\n"
"            "

#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Some of your rental products (%(product)s) cannot be rented during the\n"
"            selected period and your cart must be updated. We're sorry for the\n"
"            inconvenience.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            ສິນຄ້າເຊົ່າບາງລາຍການຂອງທ່ານ (%(product)s) ບໍ່ສາມາດເຊົ່າໄດ້ໃນໄລຍະເວລາທີ່\n"
"            ເລືອກ ແລະ ຕ້ອງໄດ້ມີການອັບເດດກະຕ່າຂອງທ່ານ. ຂໍອະໄພໃນ\n"
"            ຄວາມບໍ່ສະດວກ.\n"
"        "

